Package it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.floats

Interface Float2ShortSortedMap

All Superinterfaces:
DoubleToIntFunction, Float2ShortFunction, Float2ShortMap, Function<Float,Short>, Function<Float,Short>, Map<Float,Short>, SortedMap<Float,Short>
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractFloat2ShortSortedMap, Float2ShortAVLTreeMap, Float2ShortLinkedOpenHashMap, Float2ShortRBTreeMap, Float2ShortSortedMaps.EmptySortedMap, Float2ShortSortedMaps.Singleton, Float2ShortSortedMaps.SynchronizedSortedMap, Float2ShortSortedMaps.UnmodifiableSortedMap
public interface Float2ShortSortedMap extends Float2ShortMap, SortedMap<Float,Short>
A type-specific SortedMap; provides some additional methods that use polymorphism to avoid (un)boxing.

Additionally, this interface strengthens entrySet(), keySet(), values(), comparator(), SortedMap.subMap(Object,Object), SortedMap.headMap(Object) and SortedMap.tailMap(Object).
